title: Ebro In The Morning - Universal Hip-Hop Museum + Soulja Boy beefs with WWE-star Randy Orton 5.21.2021
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning.

In this episode, Soulja Boy guests (minute 42) to talk about his new hit-single and his beef with WWE legend Randy Orton. The crew pays homage to Biggie for his birthday (minute 18) and finish off the show with a brand new Guru segment (minute 53). 

Make sure to like and subscribe, as well as follow HOT97 on socials for all things HOT.
